snippet.title: Welcome to King Wash Laundry | E3 Guerrilla Collective Trailer
snippet.description:
PLAY, PROFIT, PURCHASE!

Subscribe: http://bit.ly/WIREDsub​
Wishlist: https://bit.ly/3tPdEse

Wired Presents: Arcade Paradise, the 90’s retro arcade adventure game. With the keys to the family laundromat, Ashley decides to transform the business and give the sleepy town of Grindstone something to get excited about! Stay one step ahead of your father, manage and invest profits, and build your very own Arcade Paradise!

Coming to PS4, PS5, Xbox One, Xbox Series S|X, Nintendo Switch and PC in 2021
